                 significantly from zero. Ten generations of selection for
                 increased rev/day resulted in an average 75\% increase in
                 activity in the four selected lines, as compared with control
                 lines. Realized heritability averaged 0.19 (range, 0.12-0.24
                 for the high-activity lines), or 0.28 when adjusted for
